"{\"uid\": \"rnz.co.nz-news-top-527174-nz-joins-space-team-operation-olympic-defender\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Pentagon directs the US-led Olympic Defender space project.Photo:AFP/ Brendan Smialowski  New Zealand has accepted a US invitation to join a top-level group that aims to deter hostile actors in space and reduce space debris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Defense\", \"score\": 0.9997541928935914, \"rank\": 0.0002458675424326814, \"text\": \"The Pentagon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Defense\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Defense\"}, {\"begin\": 69, \"end\": 72, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9989437711859976, \"rank\": 0.0010495367424853922, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 74, \"end\": 92, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brendan_Smialowski\", \"score\": 0.9999959493443569, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brendan Smialowski\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q33231\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brendan_Smialowski\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brendan_Smialowski\"}, {\"begin\": 94, \"end\": 105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.916092988798736, \"rank\": 0.07874426110075534, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 121, \"end\": 123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.8403728399966109, \"rank\": 0.1449686307376163, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The US military made the invite in April to join Operation Olympic Defender, and extended it to France and Germany, too.\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 234, \"end\": 236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.8403728399966109, \"rank\": 0.1449686307376163, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 279, \"end\": 296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Operation_Downfall\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Operation Olympic\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Operation_Downfall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Operation_Downfall\"}, {\"begin\": 297, \"end\": 305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\", \"score\": 0.6800944370323218, \"rank\": 0.4703840313172052, \"text\": \"Defender\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\"}, {\"begin\": 337, \"end\": 344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9861470569416145, \"rank\": 0.011026559301876992, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Minister of Defence Judith Collins said New Zealand would gain experience from sending a liaison officer to US Space Command for two years.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 392, \"end\": 403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.916092988798736, \"rank\": 0.07874426110075534, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Space_Command\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"US Space Command\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Space_Command\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Space_Command\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This \\\"shows New Zealand's willingness to uphold the norms of responsible behaviour in space\\\", she said in a statement on Thursday.\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 505, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.916092988798736, \"rank\": 0.07874426110075534, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The move will bring New Zealand in line with the Five Eyes intelligence grouping as Australia, the UK and Canada are already members of Olympic Defender.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 645, \"end\": 656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.916092988798736, \"rank\": 0.07874426110075534, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"score\": 0.9609081935163918, \"rank\": 0.040682142994553826, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 724, \"end\": 726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999961173671, \"rank\": 3.70388105625879e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999999740794, \"rank\": 2.4074088630051144e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Germany and France rejected a similar invite in 2021.\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 780, \"end\": 787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9861470569416145, \"rank\": 0.011026559301876992, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time around,France has made clearthat it insists on maintaining sovereign control of its space forces.\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RNZ asked Collins if New Zealand had sought a similar assurance from the Pentagon, which directs Olympic Defender.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 1058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 944, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RNZ\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}, {\"begin\": 954, \"end\": 961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.9999999997098712, \"rank\": 2.9006758107271117e-10, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}, {\"begin\": 965, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.916092988798736, \"rank\": 0.07874426110075534, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1017, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Defense\", \"score\": 0.999990030153317, \"rank\": 9.969946184678778e-06, \"text\": \"Pentagon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Defense\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Defense\"}, {\"begin\": 1049, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\", \"score\": 0.6800944370323218, \"rank\": 0.4703840313172052, \"text\": \"Defender\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This role [the liaison officer] remains under the command and control of the NZDF,\\\" Collins said.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1138, \"end\": 1142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_Defence_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NZDF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_Defence_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_Defence_Force\"}, {\"begin\": 1145, \"end\": 1152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.9999999997098712, \"rank\": 2.9006758107271117e-10, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In reports on Olympic Defender, since Space Command took it over in 2020, most of the project's focus is on its military potential.\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic Defender is a key part of a big recent US push to integrate allies into its space strategy, which aims to make it safe for civilian operations, if need be using the military space force.\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1301, \"end\": 1309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\", \"score\": 0.6800944370323218, \"rank\": 0.4703840313172052, \"text\": \"Defender\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\"}, {\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.8403728399966109, \"rank\": 0.1449686307376163, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The groupis widely seenas the \\\"highest level [of] the formal, overarching international effort to deter hostile actions in space\\\".\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Leading consultant to the Pentagon, the Rand Corporation,said this was aboutallied integration against current and future threats in space.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1646, \"end\": 1654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Defense\", \"score\": 0.999990030153317, \"rank\": 9.969946184678778e-06, \"text\": \"Pentagon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Defense\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Defense\"}, {\"begin\": 1660, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_African_rand\", \"score\": 0.9657096267643653, \"rank\": 0.035507906439120364, \"text\": \"Rand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_African_rand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_African_rand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a 2021 speech about ensuring \\\"continued space superiority\\\" over China and Russia, a US commander said: \\\"We [countries] must unite around a compelling narrative focused predominantly on the concept that we work actively to retain and strengthen our space superiority. \\\"\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1828, \"end\": 1833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999528446510251, \"rank\": 4.195802936181027e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1838, \"end\": 1844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999991168596615, \"rank\": 7.18400426147193e-07, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.8403728399966109, \"rank\": 0.1449686307376163, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The invite to New Zealand to join the project was extended in April at a defence-dominated Space Symposium in Colorado, which Collins spoke at.\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.916092988798736, \"rank\": 0.07874426110075534, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2125, \"end\": 2140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_Symposium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Space Symposium\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_Symposium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_Symposium\"}, {\"begin\": 2144, \"end\": 2152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"score\": 0.7888859389649796, \"rank\": 0.26759378175025766, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\"}, {\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.9999999997098712, \"rank\": 2.9006758107271117e-10, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Members of Olympic Defender send exchange officers to the US to work as part of the Pentagon chain of command.\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\", \"score\": 0.6800944370323218, \"rank\": 0.4703840313172052, \"text\": \"Defender\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\"}, {\"begin\": 2237, \"end\": 2239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.8403728399966109, \"rank\": 0.1449686307376163, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2263, \"end\": 2271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Defense\", \"score\": 0.999990030153317, \"rank\": 9.969946184678778e-06, \"text\": \"Pentagon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Defense\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Defense\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New Zealand's liaison officer who is going, appears to be at a lower level than that.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2290, \"end\": 2301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.916092988798736, \"rank\": 0.07874426110075534, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time US Space Command took over Olympic Defender, it said that \\\"working with Allies and Partners, [it] plans, executes, and integrates military spacepower into multi-domain global operations in order to deter aggression, defend national interests, and when necessary, defeat threats\\\".\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2389, \"end\": 2405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Space_Command\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"US Space Command\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Space_Command\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Space_Command\"}, {\"begin\": 2424, \"end\": 2432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\", \"score\": 0.6800944370323218, \"rank\": 0.4703840313172052, \"text\": \"Defender\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britten-Norman_Defender\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Collins said on Thursday that space-based technologies were essential to New Zealand's security and well-being, such as using satellite imagery to help track illegal fishing, or GPS to support our maritime supply chains.\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2670, \"end\": 2677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.9999999997098712, \"rank\": 2.9006758107271117e-10, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}, {\"begin\": 2743, \"end\": 2754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.916092988798736, \"rank\": 0.07874426110075534, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Using space assets enables better communication, faster and better-informed decision making and helps New Zealand to maintain an effective, efficient, combat capable Defence Force.\\\"\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 3074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2995, \"end\": 3006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.916092988798736, \"rank\": 0.07874426110075534, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a92024,Radio New Zealand  The fledgling national aerospace centre is in strife after failing to attract investors, underspending its budget and not making enough return on investment.Audio  Analysis -NZ is increasingly active in the US military's Space Force, but how bold can it be when America's moves to ramp up space capabilities are encased in anti-China rhetoric?\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3092, \"end\": 3109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 0.9999999947021934, \"rank\": 5.2979331399189355e-09, \"text\": \"Radio New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}, {\"begin\": 3318, \"end\": 3320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.8403728399966109, \"rank\": 0.1449686307376163, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3332, \"end\": 3343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Space_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.269674062751506e-15, \"text\": \"Space Force\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Space_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Space_Force\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"US documents show Aotearoa is increasingly aligning itself with America's big push to bring allies into its defensive and offensive space plans.\", \"from\": 3456, \"to\": 3600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3456, \"end\": 3458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.8403728399966109, \"rank\": 0.1449686307376163, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3474, \"end\": 3482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aotearoa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.106773245612156e-26, \"text\": \"Aotearoa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aotearoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aotearoa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Analysis- Space is going off, and we are involved.\", \"from\": 3602, \"to\": 3652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A US space industry event is to hear about why space-related businesses should set up shop in New Zealand.\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3656, \"end\": 3658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.8403728399966109, \"rank\": 0.1449686307376163, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3748, \"end\": 3759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.916092988798736, \"rank\": 0.07874426110075534, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"for ad-free news and current affairs  Top Stories RSS  Follow RNZ News\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 383